acking pattern when the impact is not enough to completely pierce the glass.<br />\nWhat can do Laminated Glass ?<br />\nOften laminated glass is required to provide protection against man-made threats or natural disasters such as:<br />\n…Hurricanes, <br />\n…Bomb Blasts <br />\n…Bullet-Proof<br />\n…Forcible-entry.<br />\n…UV light<br />\n…Fire-proof<br />\n…Against Noise<br />\n…Floor Panels<br />\n     ：<br />\nLaminated Glass Combination<br />\nLaminated glass is available in various forms for commercial glazing applications. To provide a wide array of design options, as well as meet various performance levels, <br />\nClear Laminated Glass (CLG)(VSG)        Tinted Laminated Glass (TLG)<br />\nReflected Laminated Glass (RLG)          Patterned Laminated Glass (PLG)<br />\nUltra Clear Laminated Glass (UCLG)       Tempered Laminated Glass (ESG)<br />\nHeat-Proof Laminated Glass (HPLG)        Bullet-Proof Laminated Glass (BPLG)<br />\nDecorative Laminated Glass (DLG)         High Strength Laminated Glass (HSLG)<br />\nLink Glass offers its PVB interlayer in four standard thicknesses: 0.38 mm (015\"), 0.76mm (.030\") ,1.14mm (.045”) and 1.52 mm (.060\"). If a stronger, more durable laminated unit is required, Tempered Glass, Heat-Strengthened Glass is recommended. <br />\n</p>','https://member.asianproducts.com/images/pmimage/6/P13680806757543189m.jpg?1368080908',0,'','','',0,'1,8,9',''),(902,'Silver Wine set-- Long-last Fortune Wine Set (ba01)','2013-08-18','<p>The shape of the wine pot is delicately made , nine spotted deer are engraved vividly. This craft will bring the long-last fortune and promising career for you !</p>','https://member.asianproducts.com/images/pmimage/7/P13766357019023817m.jpg?1376635892',0,'','','',0,'1,8,9',''),(903,'ultra-clear rolled glass (1)','2013-08-18','<p>high solar transmittance, low absorbance and higher reflectance of infrared light</p>|||<p>Specifications And Properties：<br />\n1.Thickness: 3mm～8mm; Standard: 3.2mm<br />\n2.Thic